title: 36 Female-Led Funding Startup AccelFoods Helps Other Food-Focused Startups like Soozy's Thrive
description: On this episode of The Barron Report, our host Paul Barron speaks with Jordan Gaspar, co-founder of AccelFoods, and Susan Chen, CEO of Soozy’s, a frozen, gluten-free baked good product company that has partnered with the female-led venture capitalist group in order to grow its business.
